{"tid":497210,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【回帶】伊巴:哥迪奧拿我見你一次就打你一次","createTime":"2017-12-12T13:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T15:47:34.000Z","uid":124292,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2f29a27224c2fdeb2d8dd18c0ec92728a3813f13","tid":497210,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"巴塞與AC米蘭就伊巴的先租借後出售計劃達成一致後，巴塞俱樂部請來伊巴在相關的合同上簽字。結果，伊巴將筆一扔，冷冷地表示：&ldquo;我不簽！&rdquo;這讓在場的巴塞和米蘭高層非常驚訝和尷尬。 <br />\n伊巴隨即又表示：&ldquo;除非你們轉告哥迪奧拿一句話，否則我不簽。&rdquo;巴塞和米蘭高層不知道伊布究竟要對哥迪奧拿說些什麼，而當時哥迪奧拿並不在場，於是大家問他有何話要留。伊巴的回答讓人目瞪口呆：&ldquo;我必須要說的是，在加泰羅尼​​亞我動不了他，但到了歐洲的其它地方，我以後見他一次就扁(knock-out)一次。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;knock-out&rdquo;是英語詞組，既有擊倒對手的意思，也有淘汰對手的意思。如果往好了理解，伊巴的意思是以後在賽場上碰到哥帥的球隊一次，就讓對方出局一次；如果在體育層面之外理解，伊巴的意思就是看到哥帥一次就打一次。但不管是哪種解釋，都可以看出，伊巴對哥迪奧拿是有著一肚子的怒氣。<br />\n<br />\n上帝意思係指打飛機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88154eba7927fd35af11bdaf95e779bbf2c6177","tid":497210,"uid":34993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"要人轉告<br />\n又要威又要戴頭盔"},{"pid":"c9758a2c7df7c9799ccb6fd6a145e8106f803961","tid":497210,"uid":35351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:34:22.000Z","msg":"走住黎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90d5d9625bca2ac6d8c087532687c76c1ec6d0d","tid":497210,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:54:42.000Z","msg":"波又輸左，人又唔敢打<br />\n收啦廢老"},{"pid":"393c1a06024abd8842ac162e2d46a3e2bdcad3a1","tid":497210,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:59:38.000Z","msg":"霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45fbce3066fc429ba3bb6f62908c1e167710890","tid":497210,"uid":143284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>波又輸左，人又唔敢打<br />\n收啦廢老</blockquote><br />\n你以為個個好似摩狗咁惡輸波仲走去打人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31d4d552c929ff93a4a54cc517fe44ddd6a016f","tid":497210,"uid":103947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:47:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZBFZr-AU3I0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZBFZr-AU3I0&d=d8xo9qgt%2FdGmG2m6pAbXixv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=3876412c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZBFZr-AU3I0</a><br />\n伊巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}